WEBVTT

00:02.669 --> 00:04.933
And how are you
and Tara getting along?

00:04.971 --> 00:06.632
Good.

00:06.673 --> 00:08.197
Good.

00:08.241 --> 00:10.869
Yesterday, we were
discussing Colin.

00:10.910 --> 00:13.401
I'd like to hear more.

00:13.446 --> 00:17.542
Like I told you,
we were in love,

00:17.584 --> 00:21.179
and, um, when he
started using again,

00:21.221 --> 00:23.655
it just seemed natural
that I join in,

00:23.690 --> 00:25.351
especially after
my father dumped me.

00:25.392 --> 00:26.825
Hmm.

00:26.860 --> 00:30.091
Do you think you started using
because of Colin or your father?

00:30.130 --> 00:31.995
Both, I guess.

00:32.031 --> 00:37.698
I mean, the coke was
in my drawer because of Colin,

00:37.737 --> 00:42.299
but I never would have
even thought of using it

00:42.342 --> 00:44.674
if it hadn't been
for my dad leaving.

00:44.711 --> 00:46.406
So the two men you
were counting on

00:46.446 --> 00:47.913
kind of left you high and dry,

00:47.947 --> 00:49.744
didn't they?

00:52.552 --> 00:56.318
But when I really look
at the whole thing,

00:56.356 --> 01:00.019
I realize that...

01:00.126 --> 01:02.754
I can only blame myself.

01:02.796 --> 01:04.525
How do you feel about them now?

01:06.332 --> 01:09.062
Well, where my father
is concerned,

01:09.102 --> 01:11.969
I've been through this
before with him,

01:12.005 --> 01:15.031
and, um, that's just
the way he is.

01:16.076 --> 01:17.304
I guess
maybe now it's...

01:17.343 --> 01:20.312
it's a little easier
to accept that.

01:22.048 --> 01:24.676
And I feel sort
of sorry for him.

01:26.619 --> 01:28.985
But I'll...
I'll always love him.

01:29.089 --> 01:30.488
How about Colin?

01:33.493 --> 01:35.461
I don't know.

01:37.297 --> 01:38.855
There's something about Colin

01:38.898 --> 01:43.926
that I'm really drawn to,
you know?

01:43.970 --> 01:45.961
There's something about him

01:46.005 --> 01:50.408
that just sort
of takes control over me.

01:50.443 --> 01:52.001
Do you like that?

01:57.083 --> 01:58.983
Yeah, I do.

